== A sample Facebook Rails 3 App

Using Oauth2 and the new Facebook Graph API

== Getting started

1. Get a Facebook App Api key/secret
  a. http://www.facebook.com/developers/?ref=sb add this app, if you haven't already
  b. Set up a new application http://www.facebook.com/developers/createapp.php
2. Setup your environment
  a. Install gem bundler http://gembundler.com/
  b. bundle install
  c. Put your api key/secret (from step 1) in environment.rb
3. bundle exec rails server

